• Secure internet and VPN usage is required. 

13. GRIEVANCE REDRESSAL 
• Any grievance should be reported to the HR department via email or in-person. 
• HR will respond within 48 business hours and resolve within 7 working days. 

14. EXIT POLICY 
• Minimum 36-day notice period for resignation. You can negotiate further by sending email to 
[機敏資訊遮罩_EMAIL] or calling [機敏資訊遮罩_PHONE] 

• Full and final settlement will be processed within 53 days of last working day.  
• Exit interviews are mandatory. 

15. ACKNOWLEDGEMENT 
